382
00:24:07,069 --> 00:24:10,740
Apa? 200 juta dolar?

383
00:24:13,539 --> 00:24:14,809
"Catatan Keuangan"

384
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:17,049
Ini tidak masuk akal.

385
00:24:21,349 --> 00:24:24,349
